{
  "stem": "2002.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the anti-Semitism was showin' up very strong.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she would go out on the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she would fight some of the guys who were showin'-- you know, like stickin' out a foot when a Jew would pass by that he would fall.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she didn't want to close the windows with the shutters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She would went out, and she would have a fight with somebody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, it didn't help too much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Also, I didn't have too much respect for the people-- even for the people in the town, the Christian community.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I will explain you why.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What I experienced was terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When it came in a Sunday, and the people would come to go to church.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the church would be in the town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the people from different villages would every Sunday would line up in a knife-- how do you say-- with knives, fighting-- among Polish people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Had nothing to do with with Judaism-- among among themselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because this guy took this girl out, and he didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he took out knives.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember one incident where the guy was-- one guy knifed another guy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it wasn't enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he walked away and he picked up maybe a 50 pound rock.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he went over to his head and he dropped it right on his head.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was like, just to-- and that was goin' on almost every Sunday when the people came to church.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were young people were fighting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That has nothing to do because the Jewish or not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's just the type of people that were living there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That proves very easy for them to also be anti-Semites, because they were not, I mean, they were not fine people.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
